        "Arrhenius kinetics:\n"
        "k(T) = A·exp(-E_a/(RT))\n\n"
        "Thermal damage:\n"
        "D(T) = 1 - exp(-k(T)·t)\n\n"
        "GSI(t) = GSI₀·exp(-D)\n\n"
